{"tid":203124,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"6月去塞班Saipan有咩要注意？","createTime":"2017-04-16T05:12:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-14T03:44:40.000Z","uid":35501,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f1dd73dc1df6415b65deff5449bbcc52f7b6cb12","tid":203124,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T05:12:56.000Z","msg":"6月頭去6日<br />\n諗住潛兩日水同一次sky diving<br />\n仲有其他日子有咩玩，夜晚有咩玩？<br />\n買左機票住宿，book左車<br />\n但未book潛水同sky diving，有無推介？全部fd都考左ow/aow<br />\n唔識日文去到有無問題？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f187ce10d0a0040b5bdd61d29aa513f2d5d0ef0","tid":203124,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T05:18:45.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"9a5227e6b286e61f1d86914eeadf8ccabe6bc224","tid":203124,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T06:35:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa5b301d82b8f84fc9d4f00642b2241b89a921a","tid":203124,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T06:50:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>6月頭去6日<br />\n諗住潛兩日水同一次sky diving<br />\n仲有其他日子有咩玩，夜晚有咩玩？<br />\n買左機票住宿，book左車<br />\n但未book潛水同sky diving，有無推介？全部fd都考左ow/aow<br />\n唔識日文去到有無問題？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSky diving book咗幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae8015ea59c5161f131db52b3b59dfc0161226b6","tid":203124,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T07:20:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>6月頭去6日<br />\n諗住潛兩日水同一次sky diving<br />\n仲有其他日子有咩玩，夜晚有咩玩？<br />\n買左機票住宿，book左車<br />\n但未book潛水同sky diving，有無推介？全部fd都考左ow/aow<br />\n唔識日文去到有無問題？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSky diving book咗幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未book<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過sky diving如果係高個隻，連拍片要4000幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2625c3bf7c337de2ff84c77e8b7eb1ee554b6daf","tid":203124,"uid":25954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T18:05:55.000Z","msg":"Lm<br />\n我都係五月尾六月頭去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b857c144a483bca9efddd054ce5fe0788e55cf8e","tid":203124,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:09:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Lm<br />\n我都係五月尾六月頭去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nbook左住同玩未？"},{"pid":"b06e13dc8fdaf3a433bcc176f798a88fc79e853b","tid":203124,"uid":25954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:52:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Lm<br />\n我都係五月尾六月頭去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nbook左住同玩未？</blockquote><br />\n住就book咗，玩就未<br />\n喺淘寶睇緊啲一日團，唔知會唔會中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7ea51aebd07c98bea8663dcc5cb9651ec44c4c3","tid":203124,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T15:50:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Lm<br />\n我都係五月尾六月頭去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nbook左住同玩未？</blockquote><br />\n住就book咗，玩就未<br />\n喺淘寶睇緊啲一日團，唔知會唔會中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都諗住淘寶買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5cf5adb76f6a39ca68dd429753d3dc390c26284","tid":203124,"uid":25954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T16:55:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Lm<br />\n我都係五月尾六月頭去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nbook左住同玩未？</blockquote><br />\n住就book咗，玩就未<br />\n喺淘寶睇緊啲一日團，唔知會唔會中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都諗住淘寶買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我睇嗰個小周都好似幾多好評，但諗緊幾日都book呢間定分散投資<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4ce0202b5e4b29188f65414acc0989f918c5c9b","tid":203124,"uid":57582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T21:34:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Lm<br />\n我都係五月尾六月頭去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nbook左住同玩未？</blockquote><br />\n住就book咗，玩就未<br />\n喺淘寶睇緊啲一日團，唔知會唔會中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都諗住淘寶買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n二月果時淘寶搵左間豬豬旅遊塞班地接唔錯<br />\n一日團同軍艦島都係搵佢<br />\n最緊要問野佢通常都即覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c44e2d2e2dd5d07992134755c57953af20a088d","tid":203124,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T05:46:05.000Z","msg":"搵左間叫塞班皇家<br />\n再同樓上巴打個間比較下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6659554887e2f27c12f14b843383339e44b55fb8","tid":203124,"uid":13167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T21:35:16.000Z","msg":"我2月去book左塞班皇家3日<br />\n唔錯 抵玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69d17297e09297416cb088725ff2814f8c300ce9","tid":203124,"uid":13167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T21:35:34.000Z","msg":"我2月去book左塞班皇家3日<br />\n唔錯 抵玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06659b87b9ed844ac98ad287141f0d9e09c6d6c2","tid":203124,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T03:44:40.000Z","msg":"岩岩去完， 日本仔教練， 體驗潛水一個下晏， 都係收100美金， 兼包埋教練用gopro影相拍片兼潛完番去即過相片"}]}